Gfit sorce code 

 Here is a list with descriptions:

README              This file
atom-gen            MD runner to generate atomic configurations at given conditions
basis-fun           EAM fitting basis functions
fit                 The code to fit EAM potential from the iteration matrix A
G-init              The code to calculate Gibbs free energy of given EAM potential
init                Initialization files for each iteration
pot-ite             The initial potental and potentials during iteration are stored here
rerun-code          The code to generate iteration matrix A
target              Target properties data
tools               Python tools and scripts for data processing
fit.sh              The script to run the whole fitting process    
fit.pbs             The PBS script to run the fitting on a cluster